text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria cathetoneura is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is endemic to Cuba.
text.Sources: Areces-Mallea, A.E. (1998). "Psychotria cathetoneura". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T31687A9646672. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T31687A9646672.en. Retrieved 19 December 2017.
